                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Shame is the shawl of Pink</l>
                    <l>In which we wrap the Soul</l>
                    <l>To keep it from infesting Eyes --</l>
                    <l>The elemental Veil</l>
                    <l>Which helpless Nature drops</l>
                    <l>When pushed upon a scene</l>
                    <l>Repugnant to her probity --</l>
                    <l>Shame is the tint divine.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
